comments:
I honestly did not notice anything unusual about the alien words, they were alien after all. At first, my strategy was to memorize the first 3 letters of the word because I noticed they were all different. I also tried to find a way to link the words and pictures to English words. There was one word that reminded me of the word 'sadness' and the image looked like a jar so I remembered it as the 'jar of sadness'. 

Overall, I thoroughly enjoyed this study. I just wish I had made it for the bonus :')
